{
  "stem": "11744.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's not good to be married to somebody--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, they weren't especially happy about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean-- on either side, I think, they would have liked each one of us to go-- to be part of a new family.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "20-- When I got married?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS] 23.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my husband was 25.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was working-- I was-- I wasn't working.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you did-- you could, if you wanted to, you could go to a hospital and take a morning, for instance, and be there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could do what you want.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, we are completely free to decide what you wanted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only thing that you were bound to do was to go in a war if the war breaks out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so during the war, I didn't go on the front line first.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went to the Maginot Line for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I mainly tried to form nurses to send to the front line.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as the war was not a real war-- it was what they called a phony war-- we never had really a war that was bad enough to have wounded soldier or to have bad cases.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But at the end of that phony war, after eight months, I had had formed about 25 nurses, but I couldn't send them anywhere, because there was no need them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was finally June, 1940, and that was the time when the-- the German went around the Maginot Line-- never used it, and went through Belgium and crossed into France.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And France was done in seven days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was living-- that summer of 1939, I was living at the seashore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents had taken a house on the seashore.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
